Steps to implement Heroku

1. Create a Heroku account
2. Install Heroku CLI

-------------------------
3. Create a Heroku app
4. Login to Heroku on the CLI
5. Deploy your app to Heroku

- Correcting the Port
- Procfile (which is a text file that tells Heroku how to run your app)
- Pushing to Heroku 
- Heroku Resources (Heroku Postgres, ClearDB MySQL, Redis Cloud, etc.)

Connecting to Heroku ClearDB MySQL

6. View your app in the browser

